data.description: This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. As you walk in the 2 bedrooms will be on the left with the guest bathroom upgraded sink. As you walk down the hall you will enter the living room with open concept with the kitchen and dining room. The owners suite includes tile floor in bathroom and walk-in closet, master bathroom with double sink and walk in shower. The kitchen has a modern concept with granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances, upgraded fans and lighting through home. From the Dining room there are sliding glass doors that lead out to the backyard where you can relax and entertain in backyard. Community pool and more ready for you to enjoy and be in the heart of davenport easy access to hwy 27. Grocery store .02 miles away and more. Move in ready home waiting for you. Well sought out community.
